{"tid":1331051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇球會宣佈左轉會成功,但球員體檢時失敗","createTime":"2019-07-18T20:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T01:15:18.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a39ea35d7a3321f5cf2429b8eb7fb8ddd1699fcc","tid":1331051,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:14:50.000Z","msg":"此前賓菲加已經完全敲定了佩林的交易，他的轉會本來只是時間問題。然而在體檢之後，賓菲加發現佩林的身體情況不太樂觀。目前佩林肩部有傷，他預計要在9月才能上場，球員本人也承認確實如此。<br />\n<br />\n佩林此前遭遇過兩次嚴重傷病，2016和2017年，他的膝蓋韌帶都遭遇了嚴重傷病，這也讓他長時間遠離賽場。葡媒稱賓菲加對佩林的身體情況表示懷疑，這有可能導致他的轉會告吹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab621298bbd1ec473f4530187908776c52c698a","tid":1331051,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"活基治都成功"},{"pid":"7f5e1ccf7ba991f68f633dc11f215b329fec896b","tid":1331051,"uid":59333,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:20:52.000Z","msg":"qpr個雷米 fail左利記 之後好似去左車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bea09e618c23e5262426e97a41b529a0d8ec80","tid":1331051,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"之前米蘭有個牙有問題過唔到"},{"pid":"d8ce5a26484403377cc8e1e7c1f11e1baa992621","tid":1331051,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:33:49.000Z","msg":"米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48239d6b647b715017f7aa6dc521d644056ae5dc","tid":1331051,"uid":250502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5e1ccf7ba991f68f633dc11f215b329fec896b","tid":1331051,"uid":59333,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:20:52.000Z","msg":"qpr個雷米 fail左利記 之後好似去左車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T22:36:14.000Z","msg":"費基亞去痢係咪都係體檢失敗<img sr